<sect1 id="dir_656b8020a7b0aa8521ec0615ad91cdfe_1autotoc_md483">
<title>helios::engine::modules::scene</title><para>Scene graph integration for game entities.</para>
<para>This module provides components and systems that bridge the game logic layer (GameObjects) with the rendering layer (SceneNodes).</para>
</sect1>
